# NOTE: This file references GitHub teams under the Polarityinc org
# (@polarityinc/maintainers, /storage-team, /security-team, /sre-team).
# Each team must exist with write access on the repo — if a team is
# missing GitHub silently drops the rule, so PRs touching those paths
# will merge without the intended review gate. Swap for individual
# @-handles if you don't want to manage GitHub teams.

# Default reviewers for everything.
*       @polarityinc/maintainers

# Critical paths get a second pair of eyes.
/crates/zen_storage/  @polarityinc/storage-team
/crates/zen_format/   @polarityinc/storage-team
/crates/zen_wal/      @polarityinc/storage-team
/crates/zen_compactor/  @polarityinc/storage-team
/crates/zen_auth/     @polarityinc/security-team
/.github/             @polarityinc/security-team
/deploy/              @polarityinc/sre-team
